        @RequestMapping
public org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity<org.springframework.hateoas.PagedResources<LabelColour>> showLabelColours(@RequestParam(value="pageSize",required=false)
                                                                                                                                          java.lang.Integer size,
                                                                                                                                          @RequestParam(value="page",required=false)
                                                                                                                                          java.lang.Integer page)
        Returns a ResponseEntity object containing a page of LabelColour objects, as HATEOAS PagedResources, with the optionally specified page parameters. The optional size argument specifies the page's size, must be an integer value. Defaults to '10'. The optional page argument specifies the page number. Must be an integer, Defaults to '0'

        This is mapped to the '/labelcolours' route

        Parameters:
        size - the size of pages you want returned (optional, default 10)
        page - the page number, for the given size (optional, default 0)
        Returns:
        the ResponseEntity containing the page of LabelColour PagedResources

      • createLabelColour

        @RequestMapping(method=POST)
public org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity<java.lang.Void> createLabelColour(@RequestBody
                                                                                                               LabelColour labelColour)
        Attempts to Create or Update a LabelColour in the LabelColourRepository. labelColour argument is a LabelColour object. The LabelColourRepository will attempt to save this object. If the given key value is already in use, it will update the corresponding LabelColour. Otherwise creates a new LabelColour with given values.

        Mapped to the '/labelcolours' route POST request

        Parameters:
        labelColour - the LabelColour object to be created/updated
        Returns:
        a void ResponseEntity with a NO_CONTENT status
